00:40:04,427 --> 00:40:06,168
Makanlah, dan tunggu disini.

567
00:40:06,168 --> 00:40:07,925
Kalau Ibu sudah kembali kesini,
kita nanti makan malam bersama.

568
00:40:07,925 --> 00:40:10,157
Tas dan kopi Ibu, kutinggal di sini...

569
00:40:10,157 --> 00:40:13,605
