mendaki ke tempat kau berada."

711
00:48:47,398 --> 00:48:48,780
<i>Tidak.</i>

712
00:48:48,780 --> 00:48:51,829
<i>Aku tidak butuh banyak hal.</i>

713
00:48:52,297 --> 00:48:54,862
